name: Gulom
description: To push your local changes to the remote repository, in the repository bar, click Push origin. If there are commits on the remote branch that you don't have on your local branch, GitHub Desktop prompts you to fetch new commits from the remote. In the "New Commits on Remote" window, click Fetch.
